{"response":{"verses":[{"auditid":"0","verse":"1","lastverse":"1","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.42.1","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Gen.42.1","label":"","reference":"Gen\u00e8se 42:1","prev_osis_id":"Gen.041.057,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Gen.042.002,fra-LSG","text":"<h3 class=\"s\">Les fr\u00e8res de Joseph<\/h3>\n<h5 class=\"r\">V. 1-5: cf. Ge 41:54-57. Ac 7:11, 12.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Gen.42.1\" class=\"v\">1<\/sup>Jacob, voyant qu\u2019il y avait du bl\u00e9 en \u00c9gypte, dit \u00e0 ses fils: Pourquoi vous regardez-vous les uns les autres?<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Gen.42","name":"Gen\u00e8se 42","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.42"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.42.2","name":"Gen\u00e8se 42:2","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.42.2"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.41.57","name":"Gen\u00e8se 41:57","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.41.57"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"2","lastverse":"2","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.42.2","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Gen.42.2","label":"","reference":"Gen\u00e8se 42:2","prev_osis_id":"Gen.042.001,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Gen.042.003,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Gen.42.2\" class=\"v\">2<\/sup>Il dit: Voici, j\u2019apprends qu\u2019il y a du bl\u00e9 en \u00c9gypte; descendez-y, pour nous en acheter l\u00e0, afin que nous vivions et que nous ne mourions pas.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Gen.42","name":"Gen\u00e8se 42","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.42"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.42.3","name":"Gen\u00e8se 42:3","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.42.3"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.42.1","name":"Gen\u00e8se 42:1","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.42.1"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"3","lastverse":"3","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.42.3","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Gen.42.3","label":"","reference":"Gen\u00e8se 42:3","prev_osis_id":"Gen.042.002,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Gen.042.004,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Gen.42.3\" class=\"v\">3<\/sup>Dix fr\u00e8res de Joseph descendirent en \u00c9gypte, pour acheter du bl\u00e9.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Gen.42","name":"Gen\u00e8se 42","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.42"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.42.4","name":"Gen\u00e8se 42:4","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.42.4"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.42.2","name":"Gen\u00e8se 42:2","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.42.2"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"4","lastverse":"4","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.42.4","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Gen.42.4","label":"","reference":"Gen\u00e8se 42:4","prev_osis_id":"Gen.042.003,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Gen.042.005,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Gen.42.4\" class=\"v\">4<\/sup>Jacob n\u2019envoya point avec eux Benjamin, fr\u00e8re de Joseph, dans la crainte qu\u2019il ne lui arriv\u00e2t quelque malheur.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Gen.42","name":"Gen\u00e8se 42","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.42"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.42.5","name":"Gen\u00e8se 42:5","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.42.5"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.42.3","name":"Gen\u00e8se 42:3","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.42.3"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"5","lastverse":"5","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.42.5","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Gen.42.5","label":"","reference":"Gen\u00e8se 42:5","prev_osis_id":"Gen.042.004,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Gen.042.006,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Gen.42.5\" class=\"v\">5<\/sup>Les fils d\u2019Isra\u00ebl vinrent pour acheter du bl\u00e9, au milieu de ceux qui venaient aussi; car la famine \u00e9tait dans le pays de Canaan.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Gen.42","name":"Gen\u00e8se 42","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.42"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.42.6","name":"Gen\u00e8se 42:6","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.42.6"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.42.4","name":"Gen\u00e8se 42:4","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.42.4"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"6","lastverse":"6","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.42.6","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Gen.42.6","label":"","reference":"Gen\u00e8se 42:6","prev_osis_id":"Gen.042.005,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Gen.042.007,fra-LSG","text":"<h5 class=\"r\">V. 6-24: cf. Ge 37:5-30. Job 36:8-10.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Gen.42.6\" class=\"v\">6<\/sup>Joseph commandait dans le pays; c\u2019est lui qui vendait du bl\u00e9 \u00e0 tout le peuple du pays. Les fr\u00e8res de Joseph vinrent, et se prostern\u00e8rent devant lui la face contre terre.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Gen.42","name":"Gen\u00e8se 42","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.42"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.42.7","name":"Gen\u00e8se 42:7","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.42.7"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.42.5","name":"Gen\u00e8se 42:5","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.42.5"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"7","lastverse":"7","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.42.7","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Gen.42.7","label":"","reference":"Gen\u00e8se 42:7","prev_osis_id":"Gen.042.006,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Gen.042.008,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Gen.42.7\" class=\"v\">7<\/sup>Joseph vit ses fr\u00e8res et les reconnut; mais il feignit d\u2019\u00eatre un \u00e9tranger pour eux, il leur parla durement, et leur dit: D\u2019o\u00f9 venez-vous? Ils r\u00e9pondirent: Du pays de Canaan, pour acheter des vivres.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Gen.42","name":"Gen\u00e8se 42","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.42"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.42.8","name":"Gen\u00e8se 42:8","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.42.8"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.42.6","name":"Gen\u00e8se 42:6","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.42.6"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"8","lastverse":"8","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.42.8","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Gen.42.8","label":"","reference":"Gen\u00e8se 42:8","prev_osis_id":"Gen.042.007,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Gen.042.009,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Gen.42.8\" class=\"v\">8<\/sup>Joseph reconnut ses fr\u00e8res, mais eux ne le reconnurent pas.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Gen.42","name":"Gen\u00e8se 42","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.42"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.42.9","name":"Gen\u00e8se 42:9","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.42.9"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.42.7","name":"Gen\u00e8se 42:7","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.42.7"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"9","lastverse":"9","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.42.9","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Gen.42.9","label":"","reference":"Gen\u00e8se 42:9","prev_osis_id":"Gen.042.008,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Gen.042.010,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Gen.42.9\" class=\"v\">9<\/sup>Joseph se souvint des songes qu\u2019il avait eus \u00e0 leur sujet, et il leur dit: Vous \u00eates des espions; c\u2019est pour observer les lieux faibles du pays que vous \u00eates venus.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Gen.42","name":"Gen\u00e8se 42","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.42"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.42.10","name":"Gen\u00e8se 42:10","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.42.10"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.42.8","name":"Gen\u00e8se 42:8","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.42.8"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"10","lastverse":"10","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.42.10","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Gen.42.10","label":"","reference":"Gen\u00e8se 42:10","prev_osis_id":"Gen.042.009,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Gen.042.011,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Gen.42.10\" class=\"v\">10<\/sup>Ils lui r\u00e9pondirent: Non, mon seigneur, tes serviteurs sont venus pour acheter du bl\u00e9.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Gen.42","name":"Gen\u00e8se 42","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.42"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.42.11","name":"Gen\u00e8se 42:11","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.42.11"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.42.9","name":"Gen\u00e8se 42:9","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.42.9"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"11","lastverse":"11","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.42.11","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Gen.42.11","label":"","reference":"Gen\u00e8se 42:11","prev_osis_id":"Gen.042.010,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Gen.042.012,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Gen.42.11\" class=\"v\">11<\/sup>Nous sommes tous fils d\u2019un m\u00eame homme; nous sommes sinc\u00e8res, tes serviteurs ne sont pas des espions.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Gen.42","name":"Gen\u00e8se 42","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.42"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.42.12","name":"Gen\u00e8se 42:12","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.42.12"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.42.10","name":"Gen\u00e8se 42:10","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.42.10"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"12","lastverse":"12","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.42.12","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Gen.42.12","label":"","reference":"Gen\u00e8se 42:12","prev_osis_id":"Gen.042.011,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Gen.042.013,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Gen.42.12\" class=\"v\">12<\/sup>Il leur dit: Nullement; c\u2019est pour observer les lieux faibles du pays que vous \u00eates venus.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Gen.42","name":"Gen\u00e8se 42","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.42"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.42.13","name":"Gen\u00e8se 42:13","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.42.13"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.42.11","name":"Gen\u00e8se 42:11","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.42.11"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"13","lastverse":"13","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.42.13","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Gen.42.13","label":"","reference":"Gen\u00e8se 42:13","prev_osis_id":"Gen.042.012,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Gen.042.014,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Gen.42.13\" class=\"v\">13<\/sup>Ils r\u00e9pondirent: Nous, tes serviteurs, sommes douze fr\u00e8res, fils d\u2019un m\u00eame homme au pays de Canaan; et voici, le plus jeune est aujourd\u2019hui avec notre p\u00e8re, et il y en a un qui n\u2019est plus.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Gen.42","name":"Gen\u00e8se 42","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.42"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.42.14","name":"Gen\u00e8se 42:14","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.42.14"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.42.12","name":"Gen\u00e8se 42:12","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.42.12"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"14","lastverse":"14","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.42.14","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Gen.42.14","label":"","reference":"Gen\u00e8se 42:14","prev_osis_id":"Gen.042.013,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Gen.042.015,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Gen.42.14\" class=\"v\">14<\/sup>Joseph leur dit: Je viens de vous le dire, vous \u00eates des espions.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Gen.42","name":"Gen\u00e8se 42","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.42"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.42.15","name":"Gen\u00e8se 42:15","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.42.15"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.42.13","name":"Gen\u00e8se 42:13","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.42.13"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"15","lastverse":"15","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.42.15","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Gen.42.15","label":"","reference":"Gen\u00e8se 42:15","prev_osis_id":"Gen.042.014,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Gen.042.016,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Gen.42.15\" class=\"v\">15<\/sup>Voici comment vous serez \u00e9prouv\u00e9s. Par la vie de Pharaon! Vous ne sortirez point d\u2019ici que votre jeune fr\u00e8re ne soit venu.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Gen.42","name":"Gen\u00e8se 42","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.42"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.42.16","name":"Gen\u00e8se 42:16","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.42.16"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.42.14","name":"Gen\u00e8se 42:14","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.42.14"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"16","lastverse":"16","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.42.16","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Gen.42.16","label":"","reference":"Gen\u00e8se 42:16","prev_osis_id":"Gen.042.015,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Gen.042.017,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Gen.42.16\" class=\"v\">16<\/sup>Envoyez l\u2019un de vous pour chercher votre fr\u00e8re; et vous, restez prisonniers. Vos paroles seront \u00e9prouv\u00e9es, et je saurai si la v\u00e9rit\u00e9 est chez vous; sinon, par la vie de Pharaon! Vous \u00eates des espions.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Gen.42","name":"Gen\u00e8se 42","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.42"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.42.17","name":"Gen\u00e8se 42:17","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.42.17"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.42.15","name":"Gen\u00e8se 42:15","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.42.15"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"17","lastverse":"17","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.42.17","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Gen.42.17","label":"","reference":"Gen\u00e8se 42:17","prev_osis_id":"Gen.042.016,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Gen.042.018,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Gen.42.17\" class=\"v\">17<\/sup>Et il les mit ensemble trois jours en prison.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Gen.42","name":"Gen\u00e8se 42","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.42"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.42.18","name":"Gen\u00e8se 42:18","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.42.18"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.42.16","name":"Gen\u00e8se 42:16","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.42.16"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"18","lastverse":"18","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.42.18","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Gen.42.18","label":"","reference":"Gen\u00e8se 42:18","prev_osis_id":"Gen.042.017,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Gen.042.019,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Gen.42.18\" class=\"v\">18<\/sup>Le troisi\u00e8me jour, Joseph leur dit: Faites ceci, et vous vivrez. Je crains Dieu!<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Gen.42","name":"Gen\u00e8se 42","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.42"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.42.19","name":"Gen\u00e8se 42:19","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.42.19"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.42.17","name":"Gen\u00e8se 42:17","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.42.17"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"19","lastverse":"19","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.42.19","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Gen.42.19","label":"","reference":"Gen\u00e8se 42:19","prev_osis_id":"Gen.042.018,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Gen.042.020,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Gen.42.19\" class=\"v\">19<\/sup>Si vous \u00eates sinc\u00e8res, que l\u2019un de vos fr\u00e8res reste enferm\u00e9 dans votre prison; et vous, partez, emportez du bl\u00e9 pour nourrir vos familles,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Gen.42","name":"Gen\u00e8se 42","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.42"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.42.20","name":"Gen\u00e8se 42:20","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.42.20"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.42.18","name":"Gen\u00e8se 42:18","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.42.18"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"20","lastverse":"20","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.42.20","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Gen.42.20","label":"","reference":"Gen\u00e8se 42:20","prev_osis_id":"Gen.042.019,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Gen.042.021,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Gen.42.20\" class=\"v\">20<\/sup>et amenez-moi votre jeune fr\u00e8re, afin que vos paroles soient \u00e9prouv\u00e9es et que vous ne mouriez point. Et ils firent ainsi.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Gen.42","name":"Gen\u00e8se 42","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.42"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.42.21","name":"Gen\u00e8se 42:21","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.42.21"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.42.19","name":"Gen\u00e8se 42:19","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.42.19"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"21","lastverse":"21","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.42.21","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Gen.42.21","label":"","reference":"Gen\u00e8se 42:21","prev_osis_id":"Gen.042.020,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Gen.042.022,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Gen.42.21\" class=\"v\">21<\/sup>Ils se dirent alors l\u2019un \u00e0 l\u2019autre: Oui, nous avons \u00e9t\u00e9 coupables envers notre fr\u00e8re, car nous avons vu l\u2019angoisse de son \u00e2me, quand il nous demandait gr\u00e2ce, et nous ne l\u2019avons point \u00e9cout\u00e9! C\u2019est pour cela que cette affliction nous arrive.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Gen.42","name":"Gen\u00e8se 42","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.42"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.42.22","name":"Gen\u00e8se 42:22","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.42.22"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.42.20","name":"Gen\u00e8se 42:20","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.42.20"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"22","lastverse":"22","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.42.22","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Gen.42.22","label":"","reference":"Gen\u00e8se 42:22","prev_osis_id":"Gen.042.021,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Gen.042.023,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Gen.42.22\" class=\"v\">22<\/sup>Ruben, prenant la parole, leur dit: Ne vous disais-je pas: Ne commettez point un crime envers cet enfant? Mais vous n\u2019avez point \u00e9cout\u00e9. Et voici, son sang est redemand\u00e9.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Gen.42","name":"Gen\u00e8se 42","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.42"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.42.23","name":"Gen\u00e8se 42:23","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.42.23"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.42.21","name":"Gen\u00e8se 42:21","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.42.21"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"23","lastverse":"23","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.42.23","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Gen.42.23","label":"","reference":"Gen\u00e8se 42:23","prev_osis_id":"Gen.042.022,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Gen.042.024,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Gen.42.23\" class=\"v\">23<\/sup>Ils ne savaient pas que Joseph comprenait, car il se servait avec eux d\u2019un interpr\u00e8te.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Gen.42","name":"Gen\u00e8se 42","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.42"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.42.24","name":"Gen\u00e8se 42:24","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.42.24"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.42.22","name":"Gen\u00e8se 42:22","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.42.22"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"24","lastverse":"24","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.42.24","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Gen.42.24","label":"","reference":"Gen\u00e8se 42:24","prev_osis_id":"Gen.042.023,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Gen.042.025,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Gen.42.24\" class=\"v\">24<\/sup>Il s\u2019\u00e9loigna d\u2019eux, pour pleurer. Il revint, et leur parla; puis il prit parmi eux Sim\u00e9on, et le fit encha\u00eener sous leurs yeux.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Gen.42","name":"Gen\u00e8se 42","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.42"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.42.25","name":"Gen\u00e8se 42:25","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.42.25"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.42.23","name":"Gen\u00e8se 42:23","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.42.23"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"25","lastverse":"25","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.42.25","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Gen.42.25","label":"","reference":"Gen\u00e8se 42:25","prev_osis_id":"Gen.042.024,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Gen.042.026,fra-LSG","text":"<h5 class=\"r\">V. 25-38: cf. Ro 12:17-20. Ps 53:6. Ge 37:31-35.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Gen.42.25\" class=\"v\">25<\/sup>Joseph ordonna qu\u2019on rempl\u00eet de bl\u00e9 leurs sacs, qu\u2019on rem\u00eet l\u2019argent de chacun dans son sac, et qu\u2019on leur donn\u00e2t des provisions pour la route. Et l\u2019on fit ainsi.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Gen.42","name":"Gen\u00e8se 42","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.42"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.42.26","name":"Gen\u00e8se 42:26","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.42.26"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.42.24","name":"Gen\u00e8se 42:24","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.42.24"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"26","lastverse":"26","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.42.26","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Gen.42.26","label":"","reference":"Gen\u00e8se 42:26","prev_osis_id":"Gen.042.025,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Gen.042.027,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Gen.42.26\" class=\"v\">26<\/sup>Ils charg\u00e8rent le bl\u00e9 sur leurs \u00e2nes, et partirent.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Gen.42","name":"Gen\u00e8se 42","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.42"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.42.27","name":"Gen\u00e8se 42:27","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.42.27"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.42.25","name":"Gen\u00e8se 42:25","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.42.25"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"27","lastverse":"27","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.42.27","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Gen.42.27","label":"","reference":"Gen\u00e8se 42:27","prev_osis_id":"Gen.042.026,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Gen.042.028,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Gen.42.27\" class=\"v\">27<\/sup>L\u2019un d\u2019eux ouvrit son sac pour donner du fourrage \u00e0 son \u00e2ne, dans le lieu o\u00f9 ils pass\u00e8rent la nuit, et il vit l\u2019argent qui \u00e9tait \u00e0 l\u2019entr\u00e9e du sac.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Gen.42","name":"Gen\u00e8se 42","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.42"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.42.28","name":"Gen\u00e8se 42:28","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.42.28"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.42.26","name":"Gen\u00e8se 42:26","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.42.26"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"28","lastverse":"28","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.42.28","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Gen.42.28","label":"","reference":"Gen\u00e8se 42:28","prev_osis_id":"Gen.042.027,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Gen.042.029,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Gen.42.28\" class=\"v\">28<\/sup>Il dit \u00e0 ses fr\u00e8res: Mon argent a \u00e9t\u00e9 rendu, et le voici dans mon sac. Alors leur c\u0153ur fut en d\u00e9faillance; et ils se dirent l\u2019un \u00e0 l\u2019autre, en tremblant: Qu\u2019est-ce que Dieu nous a fait?<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Gen.42","name":"Gen\u00e8se 42","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.42"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.42.29","name":"Gen\u00e8se 42:29","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.42.29"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.42.27","name":"Gen\u00e8se 42:27","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.42.27"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"29","lastverse":"29","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.42.29","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Gen.42.29","label":"","reference":"Gen\u00e8se 42:29","prev_osis_id":"Gen.042.028,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Gen.042.030,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Gen.42.29\" class=\"v\">29<\/sup>Ils revinrent aupr\u00e8s de Jacob, leur p\u00e8re, dans le pays de Canaan, et ils lui racont\u00e8rent tout ce qui leur \u00e9tait arriv\u00e9. Ils dirent:<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Gen.42","name":"Gen\u00e8se 42","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.42"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.42.30","name":"Gen\u00e8se 42:30","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.42.30"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.42.28","name":"Gen\u00e8se 42:28","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.42.28"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"30","lastverse":"30","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.42.30","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Gen.42.30","label":"","reference":"Gen\u00e8se 42:30","prev_osis_id":"Gen.042.029,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Gen.042.031,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Gen.42.30\" class=\"v\">30<\/sup>L\u2019homme, qui est le seigneur du pays, nous a parl\u00e9 durement, et il nous a pris pour des espions.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Gen.42","name":"Gen\u00e8se 42","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.42"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.42.31","name":"Gen\u00e8se 42:31","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.42.31"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.42.29","name":"Gen\u00e8se 42:29","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.42.29"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"31","lastverse":"31","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.42.31","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Gen.42.31","label":"","reference":"Gen\u00e8se 42:31","prev_osis_id":"Gen.042.030,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Gen.042.032,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Gen.42.31\" class=\"v\">31<\/sup>Nous lui avons dit: Nous sommes sinc\u00e8res, nous ne sommes pas des espions.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Gen.42","name":"Gen\u00e8se 42","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.42"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.42.32","name":"Gen\u00e8se 42:32","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.42.32"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.42.30","name":"Gen\u00e8se 42:30","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.42.30"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"32","lastverse":"32","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.42.32","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Gen.42.32","label":"","reference":"Gen\u00e8se 42:32","prev_osis_id":"Gen.042.031,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Gen.042.033,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Gen.42.32\" class=\"v\">32<\/sup>Nous sommes douze fr\u00e8res, fils de notre p\u00e8re; l\u2019un n\u2019est plus, et le plus jeune est aujourd\u2019hui avec notre p\u00e8re au pays de Canaan.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Gen.42","name":"Gen\u00e8se 42","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.42"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.42.33","name":"Gen\u00e8se 42:33","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.42.33"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.42.31","name":"Gen\u00e8se 42:31","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.42.31"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"33","lastverse":"33","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.42.33","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Gen.42.33","label":"","reference":"Gen\u00e8se 42:33","prev_osis_id":"Gen.042.032,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Gen.042.034,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Gen.42.33\" class=\"v\">33<\/sup>Et l\u2019homme, qui est le seigneur du pays, nous a dit: Voici comment je saurai si vous \u00eates sinc\u00e8res. Laissez aupr\u00e8s de moi l\u2019un de vos fr\u00e8res, prenez de quoi nourrir vos familles, partez, et amenez-moi votre jeune fr\u00e8re.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Gen.42","name":"Gen\u00e8se 42","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.42"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.42.34","name":"Gen\u00e8se 42:34","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.42.34"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.42.32","name":"Gen\u00e8se 42:32","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.42.32"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"34","lastverse":"34","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.42.34","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Gen.42.34","label":"","reference":"Gen\u00e8se 42:34","prev_osis_id":"Gen.042.033,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Gen.042.035,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Gen.42.34\" class=\"v\">34<\/sup>Je saurai ainsi que vous n\u2019\u00eates pas des espions, que vous \u00eates sinc\u00e8res; je vous rendrai votre fr\u00e8re, et vous pourrez librement parcourir le pays.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Gen.42","name":"Gen\u00e8se 42","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.42"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.42.35","name":"Gen\u00e8se 42:35","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.42.35"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.42.33","name":"Gen\u00e8se 42:33","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.42.33"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"35","lastverse":"35","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.42.35","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Gen.42.35","label":"","reference":"Gen\u00e8se 42:35","prev_osis_id":"Gen.042.034,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Gen.042.036,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Gen.42.35\" class=\"v\">35<\/sup>Lorsqu\u2019ils vid\u00e8rent leurs sacs, voici, le paquet d\u2019argent de chacun \u00e9tait dans son sac. Ils virent, eux et leur p\u00e8re, leurs paquets d\u2019argent, et ils eurent peur.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Gen.42","name":"Gen\u00e8se 42","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.42"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.42.36","name":"Gen\u00e8se 42:36","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.42.36"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.42.34","name":"Gen\u00e8se 42:34","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.42.34"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"36","lastverse":"36","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.42.36","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Gen.42.36","label":"","reference":"Gen\u00e8se 42:36","prev_osis_id":"Gen.042.035,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Gen.042.037,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Gen.42.36\" class=\"v\">36<\/sup>Jacob, leur p\u00e8re, leur dit: Vous me privez de mes enfants! Joseph n\u2019est plus, Sim\u00e9on n\u2019est plus, et vous prendriez Benjamin! C\u2019est sur moi que tout cela retombe.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Gen.42","name":"Gen\u00e8se 42","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.42"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.42.37","name":"Gen\u00e8se 42:37","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.42.37"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.42.35","name":"Gen\u00e8se 42:35","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.42.35"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"37","lastverse":"37","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.42.37","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Gen.42.37","label":"","reference":"Gen\u00e8se 42:37","prev_osis_id":"Gen.042.036,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Gen.042.038,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Gen.42.37\" class=\"v\">37<\/sup>Ruben dit \u00e0 son p\u00e8re: Tu feras mourir mes deux fils si je ne te ram\u00e8ne pas Benjamin; remets-le entre mes mains, et je te le ram\u00e8nerai.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Gen.42","name":"Gen\u00e8se 42","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.42"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.42.38","name":"Gen\u00e8se 42:38","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.42.38"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.42.36","name":"Gen\u00e8se 42:36","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.42.36"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"38","lastverse":"38","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.42.38","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Gen.42.38","label":"","reference":"Gen\u00e8se 42:38","prev_osis_id":"Gen.042.037,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Gen.043.001,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Gen.42.38\" class=\"v\">38<\/sup>Jacob dit: Mon fils ne descendra point avec vous; car son fr\u00e8re est mort, et il reste seul; s\u2019il lui arrivait un malheur dans le voyage que vous allez faire, vous feriez descendre mes cheveux blancs avec douleur dans le s\u00e9jour des morts.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Gen.42","name":"Gen\u00e8se 42","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.42"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.43.1","name":"Gen\u00e8se 43:1","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.43.1"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.42.37","name":"Gen\u00e8se 42:37","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.42.37"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"}],"meta":{"fums":"<script>\nvar _BAPI=_BAPI||{};\nif(typeof(_BAPI.t)==='undefined'){\ndocument.write('\\x3Cscript src=\"'+document.location.protocol+'\/\/d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js\"\\x3E\\x3C\/script\\x3E');}\ndocument.write(\"\\x3Cscript\\x3E_BAPI.t('5af81e8b7ace74.18420993');\\x3C\/script\\x3E\");\n<\/script><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/d3a2okcloueqyx.cloudfront.net\/nf1?t=5af81e8b7ace74.18420993\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 0; width: 0;\" \/><\/noscript>","fums_tid":"5af81e8b7ace74.18420993","fums_js_include":"d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js","fums_js":"var _BAPI=_BAPI||{};if(typeof(_BAPI.t)!='undefined'){ _BAPI.t('5af81e8b7ace74.18420993'); }","fums_noscript":"<img src=\"https:\/\/d3a2okcloueqyx.cloudfront.net\/nf1?t=5af81e8b7ace74.18420993\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 0; width: 0;\" \/>"}}}